    "description": "&quot;Balls Mania!&quot; presents you with a truly unique indie game that is 100% mouse driven with no keyboard buttons required to play the game.  It's all about avoiding the death of your balls while collecting as many blue balls as you can to survive!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse your mouse to maneuver your ball to catch the blue balls on the screen while avoiding contact with all of the red balls bouncing around the screen.  As you progress, the action will speed up and make things much more challenging.  You'll be able to snag ball goop and place it with your left mouse button in the path of fast moving enemy balls to slow them down and try and gain some control back.  Capturing a sword will allow you to slice enemy balls in half by just moving your ball near them.  Shields can also help protect you from death, but be careful because in this game, you only get one life!",
